{"id": 1428, "genre": 1001, "title": "哪些影视剧里的浪漫桥段指导了你的生活？", "description": "“为了追逐心爱的人而闯过机场安检”好像夸张了点，但总有一些很有现实意义的吧。（题图来自：Andrea Mongia）", "record_count": 3382, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170104153332rXzFm1gKcdUynBWQ.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-01-11T03:00:33Z", "options": [{"id": 152576, "content": "冬天，一个人走在海边，耳机里放着，故事细腻。不同的城市，不同的感觉，不同的风土人情。", "image": "img/option/option/20170111121119sh8S0xF1yQ7gWzcU", "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 900938}, {"id": 152832, "content": "日剧跑", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 785635}, {"id": 154368, "content": "想得到的反反复复", "image": "img/option/option/20170116110029t1rHzqU7dkXygKZw.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 906413}, {"id": 159232, "content": "边吃许留仙边接吻", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 897483}, {"id": 152577, "content": "不好看却代表了与女主同样个性的发型，臆想自己能成为男主", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 896956}, {"id": 152579, "content": "冲进大雨拦住了她告诉了我的心意。结果被拒绝了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 46, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 900957}, {"id": 154627, "content": "他离开的时候看着他的背影目送他离开", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 893533}, {"id": 156419, "content": "咬耳朵", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 911246}, {"id": 152580, "content": "但丁密码\n\n爱 . 可以唤醒一个人的灵魂和行动\n\n", "image": "img/option/option/20170111122614HcXoFjlOW5hMsqt9.jpg", "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 473509}, {"id": 152836, "content": "爱情故事指导我单身至今～", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 773952}, {"id": 152581, "content": "比如说 滚床单之前的前戏", "image": null, "praise_count": 77, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143978}, {"id": 152582, "content": "明明近在咫尺，却互相写着情书~", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 900962}, {"id": 152838, "content": "一本小说，超级教师，老书了，超热血，主人公特别有气质，我在朝他看起感兴趣可以看一看，作者张君宝", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 900283}, {"id": 152583, "content": "在电影里学会了如何对爱情精挑细选，绝不苟且！于是单身至今。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 315, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 894397}, {"id": 153863, "content": "吃晚餐停电点蜡算吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 863271}, {"id": 152584, "content": "特别喜欢周一情侣Gary对智孝说的一些话..", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 891415}, {"id": 152585, "content": "以为浪漫也会发生在自己身上。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 719650}, {"id": 154377, "content": "我让李荣浩唱给你听", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 864207}, {"id": 154889, "content": "额…很多啊比如AV…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 907212}, {"id": 152586, "content": "U jump I jump。每次坐船都会模仿", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 891415}, {"id": 152842, "content": "彭于晏在匆匆那年里面的那首《信仰》", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 902146}, {"id": 152587, "content": "“我变成另外一个张志明。”", "image": "img/option/option/20170111124120MFeBOZrgPzfkb68D.jpg", "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 491236}, {"id": 152843, "content": "单身狗表示没吃饭…", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 902148}, {"id": 153099, "content": "为自己爱的人做了很多事，但还是觉得自己没做什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 902720}, {"id": 156427, "content": "喜欢英剧里Sherlock的三观", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 432003}, {"id": 152588, "content": "爱上死傲娇", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 815906}, {"id": 152844, "content": "大家好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 902151}, {"id": 177420, "content": "冲到女厕所去抱着受了委屈而哭的她", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 842045}, {"id": 152589, "content": "用电视剧里的方式生活，怪不得单身╮(╯▽╰)╭", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 897688}, {"id": 152845, "content": "无意间", "image": "img/option/option/20170112094846BTRLj6sGnMcgKhlm.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 902151}, {"id": 152590, "content": "我养你啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 51, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 878801}, {"id": 152846, "content": "突然出现的惊喜", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 677171}, {"id": 152591, "content": "和男神躺在草坪上，晒阳光", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181115}, {"id": 152847, "content": "单身", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 902166}, {"id": 152592, "content": "从来没有过", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 494480}, {"id": 152848, "content": "以为随便遇到个人聊了几句就能啪啪啪", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 756501}, {"id": 152849, "content": "有人刚认识说了句“傻丫头”代表什么呢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 902182}, {"id": 152594, "content": "我身边的偶像剧狂热爱好者基本都没对象。", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 449558}, {"id": 152850, "content": "最近大家看孤芳不自赏剧了吗？楚钟梁好男人 超喜欢这个", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 902182}, {"id": 157458, "content": "跨越千里，大年初三坐了一天一夜的硬座火车，只为给他个生日惊喜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 838788}, {"id": 152595, "content": "过人行横道时，幻想自己在绿灯前发呆跟路人擦身而过（现实是：马上红灯了还不快走）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 319841}, {"id": 153363, "content": "明明相爱  却无法厮守", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 886233}, {"id": 152596, "content": "在对方生病的时候，跨越城市只为照顾她", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 872020}, {"id": 152854, "content": "歪个楼～不知道电视剧里有木有～但是我喜欢牵着男盆友的手睡觉～有时候早上醒来发现还牵着手，感觉暖暖的甜甜的～哈哈～虽然现在只能是回忆～但相信未来会有这么一个人～让我继续实现这种甜～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 902206}, {"id": 152599, "content": "总以为能随随便便遇到合适的人，真的是呵呵达了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 123, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 901006}, {"id": 152600, "content": "给喜欢的人写各种信", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 901011}, {"id": 156952, "content": "对女朋友跟朋友跑了已经释怀了??", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 912417}, {"id": 152601, "content": "感冒发烧，除了打电话，那个人会突然出现在清晨。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 901017}, {"id": 152602, "content": "大胆地去获得大学里喜欢的师兄的联系方式，并和他认识", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 861146}, {"id": 154138, "content": "电视剧的浪漫都是为了满足现实不能实现的幻想", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 905550}]}